要鐘意埋佢既眼光<br />\n女方唔揀你就係佢睇到一D野同你唔夾<br />\n你自己睇唔到<br />\n追唔到唔代表係壞事黎"},{"pid":"1cef24f182f74fa71d6fb4738a17148177c171c3","tid":886080,"uid":43210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:57:22.000Z","msg":"放左工，繼續吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c6061e2a346c62c85f4eb66fa69585b654c61b","tid":886080,"uid":43210,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"其實外表係最易講果part；跟手打算寫幾個topic<br />\n<br />\n點做大個pool<br />\n<br />\n第一次單對單約會有咩準備<br />\n<br />\n點get 對方對你有咩意思<br />\n<br />\n唔打算寫既：<br />\n<br />\n點媾有男朋友既女仔<br />\n<br />\n利申：每對情侶相遇都係一個奇偶，我講既野，唔跟唔一定冇女，跟足亦唔一定有；只係經驗之談，應該係會提高勝率既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbef013546c72605550cf2cb45e20eb2ae6aa8b2","tid":886080,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"見到uniqlo即刻笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995bec7179575ef73fb45a7c33a60af9aca71449","tid":886080,"uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17eb6bb2c6e35f05ba10d2c82f55fe2e2914be86","tid":886080,"uid":206382,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"1.有錢<br />\n2.靚仔<br />\n3.完！"},{"pid":"bdd28a5e540ca50feec72e0998c2a976eeba23a4","tid":886080,"uid":43210,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"做大個pool 擴闊圈子是硬道理<br />\n<br />\n有得揀，你至係老闆。只有你識得足夠數量既女仔，你才有選擇權。其實好多方法可以增大圈子，咪剩係對住部手機，出外走走啦。<br />\n<br />\n方法1: frd塔frd<br />\n<br />\n呢個最common既方法，去多d朋友聚會，人地搞生日party/boat trip party既，唔太貴咪跟埋去，總會識到d人既。去到時，如果你唔係落單既，兩個frd扯下貓尾其實都好易join到其他frds of frds 一齊玩。o岩嘴型既咪借力抄下牌囉。有咩借口都教埋你，一齊影張相